h, 40th, and 50th). A new level of Evade, VII has been added, which Thieves will receive at level 50th level.<br><br>- Backstab Critical Strikes now will almost never miss, if fighting a target monster (green, blue, yellow), and will have a much higher chance of hitting a higher level monster than they previously did.&quot;<br><br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#cccccc><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub38.ezboard.com/utrueheart78.showPublicProfile?language=EN>trueheart78</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.siscom.net/~blacklion/EQ/dance.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Disciple</span><br>  Posts: 478<br> <font color=#8b1a1a>(10/31/01 7:19:51 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm14.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=158.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.siscom.net/~blacklion/EQ/dancinghobbes.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Rogue/Friar relevant Patch Message</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> - Backstab Critical Strikes now will almost never miss, if fighting a target monster (green, blue, yellow), and will have a much higher chance of hitting a higher level monster than they previously did.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br><br>Well, can't say this will make much difference aside from solo'n, because when you're in a group it seems reds &amp; purples are more you're target than anything.  But then again 1on1 in pvp I can understand the even con match, just much more likely to be higher con.<br><br>Decent patch, good for the rogues, hope it balances em out abit more in pve. <p><DIV ALIGN="center"><IMG SRC="http://www.siscom.net/~blacklion/starspangled.gif"></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#778899><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub38.ezboard.com/urassaths.sh